<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xíng jìn zhī gē 迦南66</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 huǒ rè de xīn, huǒ rè de xīn, shéi néng zǔ dǎng wǒ men chuán fú yīn.
 wǒ men jī dū tú, cóng lái bù pà kǔ, nǎ lǐ xū yào jiù wǎng nǎ lǐ zǒu,
 bī pò hé xiū rǔ, quán bù zài hū, yào bǎ fú yīn chuán biàn quán qiú,
 xiàng qián zǒu, bù yào zài tíng liú, dà de máng máng liú xià wǒ men qián jìn de jiǎo bù,
 dà de máng máng liú xià wǒ men qián jìn de jiǎo bù.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>66</hymn_number>
</song>